steps of manicure 

step 1 - wipe off your nails with aciton 
step 2- push back your cuticles with cuticle pusher 
step 3 - remove the excess skin 
step 4- cut off the cuticle with cuticle cutter 
step 5- wipe off with aciton 
step 6 - apply nail care solution around the nails  and Massage
